    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 power plant, delivering 333hp with a 7,900 RPM redline. The individual throttle bodies provide crisp induction notes, while the high-pressure dual VANOS system ensures a broad torque curve across the rev range. Mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain sends power to the rear wheels via a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced subframe mounts and refreshed suspension bushings. The chassis maintains its factory geometry, offering the sharp, balanced handling characteristics this platform is known for. A mechanically sound and well-sorted example of an analog driving icon.",
