    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the slightest evidence of road use typical of a well-traveled car, and the body panels are straight and true. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin featuring premium upholstery that remains supple; the driver\u2019s seat shows only light softening on the bolsters, while the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. All technological features, including the navigation suite, heated seating, and premium audio system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has a documented history of on-time oil changes and recent brake service. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. It sits on a set of high-quality tires with significant tread life remaining. This is a solid, reliable choice for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle that has been garaged and respected.",
